Missile difficulties
Any discussion of missiles also involves many other issues , including international strategy and domestic civilian morale .
From the point of view of international strategy , the <ENAMEX TYPE="GPE">US</ENAMEX> clearly does not want <ENAMEX TYPE="GPE">Taiwan</ENAMEX> to develop its own offensive missile capability .
