If <ENAMEX TYPE="GPE">Taiwan</ENAMEX> were to develop long - range missiles , this would change <ENAMEX TYPE="GPE">Taiwan</ENAMEX> 's defensive posture , and alter the <ENAMEX TYPE="GPE">Taiwan</ENAMEX> - <ENAMEX TYPE="GPE">US</ENAMEX> military division of labor .
There is another possibility for <ENAMEX TYPE="GPE">Taiwan</ENAMEX> in defending against the threat of missiles from the <ENAMEX TYPE="GPE">PRC</ENAMEX> .
