This is a key area of development for the future in which <ENAMEX TYPE="GPE">Taiwan</ENAMEX> can rely on itself and need not be limited by what can be procured abroad .
Construction of a complete defense system is essential , but the highest form of military strategy is still to defeat the enemy without firing a shot .
In fact , the pro-active defense <ENAMEX TYPE="GPE">Taiwan</ENAMEX> is currently studying is a way of pursuing peace .
